Package: ACV
Title: Time-Series Cross-Validation Loss Estimation and Testing with Optimal Affine Weighing
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Filip",
           family = "Stanek",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stanek.fi@gmail.com")
Description: Package ACV offers improved time-series cross-validation loss estimator which utilizes also in sample contrasts via optimal affine weighing scheme to achieve higher precision of the estimates. It also offers improved versions of Diebold-Mariano and Ibragimov-Muller test of equal predictive ability which offers more power than their standard counterparts.
